324
00:21:46,752 --> 00:21:49,220
I think we gotta end the freeze-out.

325
00:21:51,557 --> 00:21:53,388
Wait. Is this for real?

326
00:21:53,626 --> 00:21:55,457
Yeah. Check out the ring.

327
00:21:56,261 --> 00:21:58,388
Oh, my God!

328
00:21:59,198 --> 00:22:01,723
So you two are really serious?

329
00:22:03,602 --> 00:22:05,433
Yeah, pretty much.

330
00:22:06,138 --> 00:22:08,766
You're gonna get married?

331
00:22:09,808 --> 00:22:12,538
We're gonna be brothers-in-law!
Come here!

332
00:22:13,812 --> 00:22:16,576
And we're gonna be friends again.

333
00:22:18,784 --> 00:22:20,046
What?

334
00:22:20,252 --> 00:22:23,153
-Water under the bridge! Forget it!
-Okay.

335
00:22:24,023 --> 00:22:27,550
I was gonna wait till it was official,
but I had to tell you guys.

336
00:22:27,793 --> 00:22:29,556
You're my best friends.

337
00:22:29,728 --> 00:22:31,218
-I can't believe this.
-Me too.

338
00:22:31,430 --> 00:22:35,890
I was planning on having a conversation
with you about your intentions.

339
00:22:37,002 --> 00:22:38,936
I think I'm gonna cry.

340
00:22:39,104 --> 00:22:41,334
Oh! No more crying!

341
00:22:41,573 --> 00:22:44,542
I just dumped one crybaby.
I'll dump you too.

342
00:22:46,578 --> 00:22:49,012
I'm gonna ask Monica to marry me.

343
00:22:49,448 --> 00:22:51,109
Oh, my God!

344
00:22:51,383 --> 00:22:53,010
Oh, my God!

345
00:22:53,252 --> 00:22:56,449
Oh, Chandler!
You guys are gonna be so happy!

346
00:22:56,722 --> 00:22:59,850
-I know.
-Where's all the tissues?!

347
00:23:02,761 --> 00:23:07,221
-Check out the ring.
-Oh, nice. One and a half carat, easy.

348
00:23:09,068 --> 00:23:10,160
-Hey.
-Hey, Pheebs.

349
00:23:10,469 --> 00:23:14,098
-He's gonna ask Monica to marry him.
-I helped pick out the ring.

350
00:23:17,643 --> 00:23:20,510
You told her before you told us?

351
00:23:21,380 --> 00:23:26,113
She walked in while I was looking at
brochures. You can understand that.

352
00:23:27,786 --> 00:23:29,219
Guys?

353
00:23:31,990 --> 00:23:33,355
Guys?

354
00:23:40,399 --> 00:23:44,062
God, that ring Chandler picked out
was so beautiful.

355
00:23:44,269 --> 00:23:47,204
You should know.
You've bought like a billion of them.

356
00:23:49,742 --> 00:23:52,404
Humor based on my pain.

357
00:23:54,613 --> 00:23:56,137
You know what's funny?

358
00:23:56,315 --> 00:23:59,614
